WEBVTT

00:05.573 --> 00:09.376
It's easily the most contentious
piece of real estate

00:09.377 --> 00:09.910
in the world.

00:09.911 --> 00:11.611
And there's no hope, none, of

00:11.612 --> 00:18.618
ever talking about it without
pissing somebody, if not

00:18.619 --> 00:19.320
everybody off.

00:19.321 --> 00:20.720
Maybe that's why it's taken me

00:20.721 --> 00:21.821
so long to come here, a place

00:21.822 --> 00:23.456
where even the names of ordinary

00:23.457 --> 00:27.094
things are ferociously disputed.

00:27.095 --> 00:29.262
Where does falafel come from?

00:29.263 --> 00:31.264
Who makes the best hummus?

00:31.265 --> 00:32.999
Is it a fence or a wall?

00:33.000 --> 00:34.767
By the end of this hour, I'll be

00:34.768 --> 00:37.670
seen by many as a terrorist

00:37.671 --> 00:40.607
sympathizer, a Zionist tool, a

00:40.608 --> 00:42.809
self-hating Jew, an apologist

00:42.810 --> 00:44.844
for American imperialism, an

00:44.845 --> 00:50.083
orientalist, socialist,
fascist, CIA agent, and worse.

00:50.084 --> 00:52.085
So here goes nothing.

00:52.086 --> 00:57.057
♪

